00:22:15.500 --> 00:22:17.210
Hindi pa ako ganoon katagal.

00:22:18.795 --> 00:22:23.508
Isang araw, anim na oras at pitong minuto,
parang walang hanggan sa akin.

00:22:38.565 --> 00:22:41.026
Where's Matmat?

00:22:43.153 --> 00:22:44.696
Naka-isolate pa rin?

00:22:51.286 --> 00:22:52.579
Hindi pa rin siya lalabas?

00:22:54.289 --> 00:22:55.832
Hindi pa kami nag-uusap.

00:22:59.711 --> 00:23:02.714
Kung ayaw niyang
lumabas, ibig sabihin lang...

00:23:04.299 --> 00:23:06.051
hindi pa siya handang kausapin ako.

00:23:06.134 --> 00:23:07.135
Patrick.

00:23:09.221 --> 00:23:11.181
Wala sa mga ito ang nangyari

00:23:11.807 --> 00:23:13.767
kung hindi ka naging close ni Mia.

00:23:17.312 --> 00:23:18.271
Bro.

00:23:18.939 --> 00:23:21.483
Tingnan mo ang iyong palad.

00:23:24.486 --> 00:23:28.031
Baka ipaalala lang sayo
kung bakit hindi mo dapat kasama si Mia.

00:23:31.785 --> 00:23:33.036
alam ko yun.

00:23:38.750 --> 00:23:40.502
Panaginip lang pala.

00:23:43.213 --> 00:23:44.840
At sa panaginip na iyon,

00:23:46.299 --> 00:23:47.801
masaya ako.

